rows.label: qst202013_msg001
rows.name:
We hid those bracers in the Ruins of
Fountain Park.

rows.label: qst202013_msg002
rows.name:
It was a long time ago, so my memory
is a little hazy...

rows.label: qst202013_msg003
rows.name:
But I'm quite confident about this.
We walked a short way down a side
road and hid it around there.

rows.label: qst202013_msg0101
rows.name:
Dofusay has two children, a son and
a daughter.

rows.label: qst202013_msg0102
rows.name: Ohh, it really brings back memories.

rows.label: qst202013_msg0103
rows.name:
I haven't seen them for quite
some time. I imagine they're all
grown up now.

rows.label: qst202013_msg0104
rows.name:
They must be taller than Torigo's
windmill by now, surely...

rows.label: qst202013_msg0105
rows.name:
Well, they do say that growing
as a person is a lifelong journey,
don't they?

rows.label: qst202013_msg0106
rows.name: Ha ha! I'm joking, of course!
